ideas.title: Swan Street Stampede
ideas.premise: A flock of swans are shown stampeding down Swan Street, fleeing a tram after hearing the sports team won.
ideas.why_funny: Playing on Melbourne's swan population and passionate (sometimes over-the-top) sports fans.

ideas.title: Four Seasons in One Cartoon
ideas.premise: A panel cartoon shows four panels, each representing one of Melbourne's infamous 'four seasons in one day'.
ideas.why_funny: Relatable to Melburnians' experience with unpredictable weather, exaggerating the quick changes.

ideas.title: Booming Espresso Expansion
ideas.premise: A small Melbourne cafe is depicted literally 'expanding' like a balloon due to overwhelming coffee demand.
ideas.why_funny: Pokes fun at Melbourne's strong coffee culture and booming small businesses.

ideas.title: The Arts Centre Spire's Selfie Stick
ideas.premise: The Arts Centre Spire has a ridiculously long selfie stick taking photos of the crowded community event below.
ideas.why_funny: Satirizes touristy selfie culture using a Melbourne landmark.

ideas.title: Level Crossing Removal Rampage
ideas.premise: A giant robot (representing the infrastructure project) is malfunctioning and knocking down level crossings at random.
ideas.why_funny: Exaggerates the disruption caused by the ongoing level crossing removal project in Melbourne.
